text: Muslimabad or Muslim Abad is a village and Union Council of Mardan District in the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa province of Pakistan. It is at 34°23'0N 71°54'5E and has a height of 379 metres (1246 feet).Location of Muslim Abad == References == Category:Union councils of Mardan District
title: Muslimabad (Mardan)
